:"鳩鐵條數都未諗掂,得撚閒理你班升斗市民咩"},{"pid":"8a19a8f11ab827e5f61dca33e159b6032cd53492","tid":795063,"uid":197134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T04:03:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}